		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/at-what-age-does-alzheimers-disease-begin-mayo-clinic-study-points-to-changes-decades-before-symptoms/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[kelseyriegler]]></dc:creator>
