		<title>Mayo Clinic research supports targeted therapy to manage kidney complications, potentially enabling continuation of lifesaving immunotherapy</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-research-supports-targeted-therapy-to-manage-kidney-complications-potentially-enabling-continuation-of-lifesaving-immunotherapy/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Jessica Saenz]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 13:43:03 +0000</pubDate>
