		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-researcher-awarded-breakthrough-prize-for-als-dementia-gene-discovery/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Lynda De Widt]]></dc:creator>
